I"©<p>The oligo database currently hosts oligo sequences of six species, including Arabidopsis, rice, maize, potato, barley and soybean. The details of the oligos are showed in the bellow table.<br />
To download the oligos, please click the download link of the speices. Details about <a href="#chorus_def">Chorus2</a>, which was used to design the oligos can be found <a href="https://github.com/zhangtaolab/Chorus2">here</a>.</p>

